{"word":"ἀπολούω","slug":"ἀπολούω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπολούω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to wash off</i> dirt, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <el>ἅλμην ὤμοιν ἀπολούεσθαι</el> <i>to wash</i> the brine <i>from off my</i> shoulders, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to wash clean</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:— <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to wash oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> et rei, <el>Πάτροκλον λοῦσαι ἄπο βρότον</el> <i>to wash</i> the gore <i>off</i> him, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}